Title: World Bank team lead
Description: The lead of the World Bank project that created and/or used the dataset. Also known as the Task Team Leader (TTL).

Title: Resource provider
Description: An entity that supplies the resource.

Title: Custodian
Description: An entity that accepts accountability and responsibility for the resource and ensures appropriate care and maintenance of the resource.

Title: Owner
Description: An entity that owns the resource.

Title: User
Description: An entity who uses the resource.

Title: Distributor
Description: An entity who distributes the resource.

Title: Principal investigator
Description: A key entity responsible for gathering information and conducting research.

Title: Processor
Description: An entity who has processed the data in a manner such that the resource has been modified.

Title: Author
Description: An entity who authored the resource.

Title: Sponsor
Description: An entity who speaks for the resource.

Title: Co-author
Description: An entity who jointly authors the resource.

Title: Collaborator
Description: An entity who assists with the generation of the resource other than the principal investigator.

Title: Editor
Description: An entity who reviewed or modified the resource to improve the content.

Title: Mediator
Description: A class of entity that mediates access to the resource and for whom the resource is intended or useful.

Title: Rights holder
Description: An entity owning or managing rights over the resource.

Title: Contributor
Description: An entity contributing to the resource.

Title: Funder
Description: An entity providing monetary support for the resource.

Title: Stakeholder
Description: An entity who has an interest in the resource or the use of the resource.

Title: publisher
Description: publisher
